weather

Interface WeatherReading

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    StevensonReading

    public interface WeatherReading
    A WeatherReading represents the data that is collected at a variety of weather stations. Classes that implement this interface will vary depending upon the type of weather station that does the reading.
